DESCRIPTION >
    Store comments with sentiment analysis results including sentiment score and classification

SCHEMA >
    `comment_id` UUID `json:$.comment_id`,
    `sentiment_score` Float32 `json:$.sentiment_score`,
    `sentiment_label` String `json:$.sentiment_label`,
    `confidence_score` Float32 `json:$.confidence_score`,
    `analyzed_at` DateTime `json:$.analyzed_at`

ENGINE "MergeTree"
ENGINE_SORTING_KEY "comment_id"